                            <div class="screen">

                                <div class="col-md mt-5">
                                    <div class="card" style="width:100%; background-color:lightgrey; border:dashed; border-color:darkblue">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <h5 class="card-title" style="color:darkblue">Try adding a wallet</h5>
                                            <p style="color:darkblue; font-size:14px">WALLETS</p>
                                            <ul class="card-text" style="color:darkblue; font-size:14px">
                                                <li>When a wallet is created, a unique public and private key is created for the user</li>
                                                <li> A wallet can be a node or computer that is part of the network</li>
                                                <li></li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <p style="color:darkblue; font-size:14px">TRANSACTIONS</p>
                                            <ul class="card-text" style="color:darkblue; font-size:14px">
                                                <li>When a wallet is created, a unique public and private key is created for the user</li>
                                                <li> A wallet can be a node or computer that is part of the network</li>
                                                <li>Miners to mine blocks to verify transactions are valid and if they mine the next block they will add a new block of transactions to the blockchain</li>
