                                                <li>The information in a block is predetermined so the only property you can change is the nonce, you keep changing the nonce until you get a hash which has the correct number of leading zeroes</li>
                                                <li>A blockchain can exist without cryptocurrency. Crytocurrency provides incentive for nodes to mine blocks.</li>
                                                <li>The purpose of mining a block, is to verify to that a transaction is valid, and to include the transaction information in a block in the blockchain.</li>
